name: MINA
tagline: A tool for content creation, storage and sharing
body:
MINA is a tool designed for the creation, storage and sharing of content. It is currently being designed and created as an Honours' Project at the University of Cape Town for Praekelt Foundation by Codie Roelf and Cuthbert Chidoori.

Literature Review: <https://github.com/>

Proposal: <http://codiebeulaine.github.io/unicore-noname/MoloProposal.pdf>
